query:
SELECT
                        puzzle_id, variant_id, program_material,
                        Count(DISTINCT solver_id) as count
                        FROM VerifiedSpeedSolve
                        WHERE average = $1
                            AND blind = $2
                            AND filters <= CASE
                                    WHEN $3 THEN $4
                                    ELSE primary_filters
                                END
                            AND macros <= CASE
                                    WHEN $5 THEN $6
                                    ELSE primary_macros
                                END
                            AND one_handed >= $7
                            AND NOT (($4 OR $6) AND program_material)
                        GROUP BY puzzle_id, variant_id, program_material
